objects.description: FIN8's malicious spearphishing payloads use WMI to launch malware and spawn cmd.exe execution. (Citation: FireEye Obfuscation June 2017) FIN8 has also used WMIC during (Citation: Lateral Movement) and post compromise cleanup activities. (Citation: FireEye Know Your Enemy FIN8 Aug 2016)
